OL,3,C'Hannah won't be silenced' after Green
OL,4,CMP targeted in Manchester
OL,6,FThe Green Party has hit out after a
OL,7,Fgroup of 'angry men' targeted Gorton
OL,8,Fand Denton MP Hannah Spencer in
OL,9,FManchester, forcing her to be ushered
OL,10,Finto a police car.
OL,12,FThe 34-year-old was given a police
OL,13,Fescort away from Piccadilly Gardens
OL,14,Fafter clashes at an anti-far right
OL,15,Fevent on March 8.
OL,17,FThe MP was taken to a waiting police
OL,18,Fcar after several scuffles broke out
OL,19,Ffollowing her appearance at the
OL,20,FGreater Manchester Together Alliance
OL,21,Fdemo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
