OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773144736
OL,3,C'Hannah won't be silenced' after Green
OL,4,CMP targeted in Manchester
OL,6,FAnti-racism campaigners gathered in
OL,7,FPiccadilly Gardens for the launch of
OL,8,Fthe local branch of the nationwide
OL,9,Fgroup, which is organising a 'March to
OL,10,Fstop the far right' in London.
OL,12,FFootage posted widely online from a
OL,13,Fnumber of different accounts showed
OL,14,Fthat as Ms Spencer walked away
OL,15,Ffollowing her speech, she was
OL,16,Fquestioned and followed before chaotic
OL,17,Fscenes broke out.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
