PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773144736
OL,3,C'Hannah won't be silenced' after Green
OL,4,CMP targeted in Manchester
OL,6,FShe was questioned by a YouTuber
OL,7,Fwearing a 'Trans women are men'
OL,8,Fsandwich board, who repeatedly asked
OL,9,F'Are trans women women?'. Two men then
OL,10,Fbegan arguing as punches were thrown
OL,11,Fbefore a police officer intervened.
OL,13,FOne of the men then became involved in
OL,14,Fa separate altercation with a woman,
OL,15,Fas several others stepped in.
OL,17,FMore punches were thrown as another
OL,18,Ffracas broke out between a number of
OL,19,Fpeople and others as police tried to
OL,20,Fseparate the two sides.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
