PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773144736
OL,3,C'Hannah won't be silenced' after Green
OL,4,CMP targeted in Manchester
OL,6,FA Green Party Spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Hannah was talking today in
OL,8,FManchester about community cohesion
OL,9,Fand unity. A few angry men, attempting
OL,10,Fto spread anti-trans bigotry, and
OL,11,Fchose this moment to try to silence
OL,12,Fand harass Hannah.
OL,14,F"There is a bitter irony that today,
OL,15,Fon International Women's Day, these
OL,16,Ffew men claiming to 'protect women'
OL,17,Fbehaved like this towards parliament's
OL,18,Fnewest female MP, chasing her to a
OL,19,Fpolice car.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773144736
OL,3,C'Hannah won't be silenced' after Green
OL,4,CMP targeted in Manchester
OL,6,F"Worse still, some of the abuse faced
OL,7,Fby Hannah included the same
OL,8,Fmisinformation and outright lies
OL,9,Fshared by her political opponents
OL,10,Fonline.
OL,12,F"Hannah won't be silenced and will
OL,13,Fcontinue to speak up for the
OL,14,Fcommunities that she has been elected
OL,15,Fto represent."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
