OL,3,C'Hannah won't be silenced' after Green
OL,4,CMP targeted in Manchester
OL,6,FEarlier in the afternoon, Ms Spencer
OL,7,Fhad told the Together Alliance: "It's
OL,8,Fabout a movement of people coming
OL,9,Ftogether, finding common ground,
OL,10,Fgetting together, working together,
OL,11,Fmobilizing and defeating politics of
OL,12,Fhatred and division.
OL,14,F"And last week we did exactly that. We
OL,15,Fshowed Greater Manchester at its
OL,16,Ffinest and we kicked out people who
OL,17,Fare here to stir hatred."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
