OL,3,C'Hannah won't be silenced' after Green
OL,4,CMP targeted in Manchester
OL,6,FMs Spencer was elected as the Green
OL,7,FParty's first MP in the north of
OL,8,FEngland after her decisive victory in
OL,9,Fthe Gorton and Denton by-election on
OL,10,FFebruary 27. Greater
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
